{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_10_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 こ、こころのプリンが！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、こころ。最近、今まで以上に頑張ってるな\n現場が一緒だった仕事相手の人達も、褒めてたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Kokoro. You've been working harder than ever lately.\nEven the people you worked with at the venue were praising you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。こころは謙虚ですから\nBIG4になったからって、調子に乗ったりしません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Kokoro is humble.\nJust because I became BIG4 doesn't mean I'll get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7359409015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "偉くなった途端に態度を変えて、評判を下げる\n……そんな小物ムーブ、こころがすると思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The moment they get a big head‚ they change their attitude and ruin their reputation.\n…Do you think Kokoro would make such a small-time move?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7359409015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うん、それもそうだな……\nじゃあ、学校生活の方はどうなんだ？　勉強とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right‚ that makes sense…\nThen‚ how is your school life? Like studying and stuff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですか急に。勉強……は、まぁ、それなりです\n大丈夫、じゃないかと思いますよ？　多分……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what is it‚ so suddenly? Studying… well‚ it's so-so.\nI think it's probably fine? Maybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5398851395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "怪しいぞ。BIG4になって仕事が大幅に増えたろ？\n学校に行けない日が増えてるし、気になってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds suspicious. Your workload increased significantly after becoming BIG4‚ right?\nThe days you can't go to school have increased‚ and I'm worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こころの仕事を\n少しセーブした方がいいんじゃないかと思ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we should\nlimit Kokoro's workload a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえいえ！　そんな必要全然ありませんよ\nこころは今、凄く充実してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no! There is absolutely no need for that.\nKokoro is feeling very fulfilled right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3803430398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "仕事をセーブする必要なんてありません\nむしろ、もっと沢山入れてほしいくらいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no need to limit my work.\nIf anything‚ I'd like even more work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6803430398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるよ。だが、アイドルだからといって\n学生としての生活や勉強をおろそかにしないでほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel. But just because you're an idol‚\nI don't want you to neglect your life as a student or your studies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "学校の試験、もうすぐだろ？\n仕事と学業は両立させないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "School exams are coming up soon‚ right?\nYou have to balance both work and school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……そんな偉そうなこと言うってことは\n{user}さんにも覚悟はあるんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… If you're going to say such lofty things‚\nthen {user}-san‚ you are also prepared‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4789830048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、なんの覚悟だ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ prepared for what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7628631317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こころが仕事と学業を両立させるために\n全力でサポートする覚悟、ですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The resolve to fully support Kokoro\nto balance both work and school‚ you see?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8791872341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "仕事をセーブして勉強に専念するようでは\n『両立』なんて、言えませんよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you limit my work so I focus only on studying‚\nyou can't really call that 'balancing' them‚ right~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4791872341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "なら仕事量は今のままで、{user}さんが\nこころの勉強を見るのが筋ってものじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ keep the current workload‚ and it makes sense that {user}-san\nshould supervise Kokoro's studies‚ wouldn't you agree?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1125205675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "もっとも、お忙しい{user}さんに\nそんな時間があるとは思えませんけど～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although‚ I doubt that a busy {user}-san\nwould have time for that~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2125205675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな、こころの言う通りだ\nよし、俺と一緒に頑張ろう。ひとまず今度の試験までだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right‚ Kokoro.\nAlright‚ let's work hard together. Just until the next exam for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "え。……で、でも、{user}さんだって\nお仕事で忙しいですよね？　無理しなくても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh. …B-but‚ {user}-san is busy\nwith work‚ aren't you? You don't have to overdo it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3220253626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の休憩時間と移動時間もフルに使えば\n勉強時間は確保出来るし、後はこころのやる気次第だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I make full use of my work breaks and travel time‚\nI can secure time for studying‚ and the rest depends on your motivation‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "こころのやる気なら、たった今ゼロになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for Kokoro's motivation‚ it just hit zero this very moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.0751700446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、相変わらず冗談がうまいな、こころは\nそれじゃ、試験に向けて今日から頑張ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ you're as good at joking as ever‚ Kokoro.\nAlright then‚ let's start working hard for the exam today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～？　いきなり今日からですか～？\n……はぁ、余計なこと言っちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeh~? Starting today‚ just like that~?\n…Haa‚ I said something unnecessary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.791881116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、ポジティブに考えましょう。これなら\n学校に行かなくても、成績をキープ出来るのでは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ let's think positively. If this is the case‚\nI might be able to maintain my grades without even going to school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.991881116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（学校にもちゃんと行ってもらうんだが……）\n（こころって、そんなに学校が嫌いだったのか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She still has to go to school properly‚ though…）\n（Was Kokoro really that averse to school…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『星見フレンドフェス』参加決定後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After deciding to participate in the \"Hoshimi Friend Fes\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.1206118589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 186.9206220315
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、例のkanaさんと組んでもらう\n『ニコイチ仲良しユニット決定戦』の件なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ regarding that matter of you teaming up with Kana-san—\n\"Two-in-One Besties Unit Showdown\" thing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、その節は、ご心配をおかけしました～\n今はkanaさんとこころで、仲良く頑張ってますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I apologize for causing you trouble back then~\nNow kana-san and Kokoro are getting along well and doing their best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.2194550511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "私達二人を共演NGにしそうになるくらい\n悩ませちゃったんですよね？　すみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To the point where you almost made our pairing forbidden\nyou were worried‚ right? I apologize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.7194550511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……随分しおらしいな。大体、あんなに嫌がってたのに\nどうして急に組むことになったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're awfully meek. Besides‚ you hated it so much before.\nWhy did you suddenly agree to team up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "別に何もありませんよ？　ケンカするほど仲がいいって\n言うじゃないですか～。最初のは軽いじゃれ合いですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing in particular happened‚ you see? They say the closer you are‚ the more you fight.\nThat's what they say‚ right~? The first part was just light teasing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.2886160211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "それにこころはBIG4ですから。元BIG4の\nkanaさんのことくらい、受け止めてあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Kokoro is BIG4. I can afford to accept\na former BIG4 like Kana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.0886160211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、狙いは冠番組か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Could your target be the flagship show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.5162232285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "冠番組……？　あ～、優勝したユニットがもらえる\n特典ですよね。それが何か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Flagship show…? Ah‚ that's the prize that the winning unit gets‚\nright? Is there something wrong with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.7003169533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "その冠番組が目当てで、無理やり二人で\n仲がいいフリをしてるだけ……なんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're only after that flagship show‚ and you're forcing yourselves\nto pretend to be on good terms… isn't that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、おかしな{user}さんですね～\n誰だって、冠番組はほしいに決まってるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ you're so strange‚ {user}-san~\nOf course everyone wants a flagship show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.9746934092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "別にkanaさんとこころに限った話じゃないです\nみんなそうじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a story limited to just Kana-san and Kokoro.\nIsn't everyone like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.9413600758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "それにkanaさんとこころは本当に仲良しですよ～？\nこころはkanaさんのことリスペクトしてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Kana-san and Kokoro are truly close‚ you know~?\nKokoro respects Kana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.1413600758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "それともなんですか？　{user}さんは\nこころ達のこと、根拠もなく疑ってるんですか？",
