      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "そこでこころ達が、息ピッタリのトークを披露出来たら\n疑り深い{user}さんも信じてくれます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Kokoro and I can demonstrate perfectly synchronized talk there‚\nwill even the skeptical {user}-san believe us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.0247327641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。それなら俺にだって文句はない\n……言いくるめられたような気もするけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. In that case‚ I have no complaints.\n…I also feel like I've been talked into it.",
