      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "気のせいですって。それじゃこころは\n次の仕事があるので、そろそろ失礼しま～す",
      "translations": {
